text: Alençon is a commune. It is found in the Orne department in the north western of France. ==Sister cities== Alençon is twinned with: * Basingstoke, United Kingdom, since 1968 * Quakenbrück, Germany, since 1969 * Koutiala, Mali, since 1970 Category:Communes in Orne Category:Departmental capitals in France
title: Alençon
